Package: surveyframe
Title: A Survey Instrument Workflow for Design, Deployment, Scoring, and Reporting
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      given = "Mohammed Ali",
      family = "Sharafuddin",
      email = "mas@flairmi.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Defines a survey instrument as a first-class R object and provides
    a full workflow from instrument design through data collection, quality
    checking, scoring, psychometric diagnostics, and reproducible reporting.
    The SurveyStudio interface, launched with launch_studio(), provides a
    visual shell for the complete pipeline. Instruments are saved as
    human-readable JSON files with a SHA-256 integrity hash.
